          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "4"
        },
        "To Titus, a true son in our common faith:\n",
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "5"
        },
        "For this purpose I left you in Crete, that you would set in order things unfinished."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "chapter",
      "marker": "c",
